text.tspan: We are honored to extend our gratitude for participation in Codefreeze 2024 which took
place in Kiilop, Finland from Saturday, 6. January to Saturday, 13. January 2024 to
Codefreeze is a yearly, non-profit, international unconference for open-minded Software
Crafters and Testers who want to improve their craft and the software industry as a whole.
It is organised by members of the Software Crafters Community (softwarecrafters.org), the
conference attracts participants from all over the world.
